Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fad(1000,1000)\fsp46\bord0\pos(192,120)\b0}地球脉{\fsp3}动  III
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人正在寻找\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}These people are hunting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上最濒危的动物之一\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}for one of the most endangered animals on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,黑犀 一种因犀角而遭到偷猎的动物\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}The black rhino - an animal poached for its horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些人并不会伤害它\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}But they aren't going to harm her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,杜米 · 兹瓦内和他的团队正在执行救援任务\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Dumi Zwane and his team are on a rescue mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}我永远不会放弃为犀牛而战的信念\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}I don't think I'll ever stop fighting for rhino.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}这是我的使命\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}It's just not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}好了\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}OK! Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们正在安全保护区建立一个新的繁殖群\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}They're setting up a new breeding colony in a safe haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}放在二号吊索上\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Get her on two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.68,0:01:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}二号吊索 很好\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Two. OK. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这只雌性黑犀将成为繁殖群的核心\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}This female is going to be at the very centre of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它重逾一吨\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}She weighs over a tonne...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}出发\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一种办法才能把它运走\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..and there's only one way to get her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}很好\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}就是这样 很好\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}There we are. Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}看着它这样飞走 我心情非常激动\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}When I watch it fly off, it's very emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}是一种无与伦比的感觉\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}It's a beautiful feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它被注射了镇静剂 很安全\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}She is sedated and safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,半小时内便会返回地面\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}...and in less than half an hour, she'll be back on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个可能拯救整个物种的项目中 开始属于它的新生活\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and starting a new life in a project that could save her entire species,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切都要感谢杜米和他的优秀团队\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}thanks to Dumi and his remarkable team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\bord0\fad(3000,3000)\pos(192,210)\b0}家    园    卫    士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs10\fad(1000,3000)\bord0\pos(192,250)\b0}旁  白\N{\fs14\bord0\b0}大卫 · 爱登堡  爵士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,220)}在20年前 我们开始制作\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}We started making the very first Planet Earth series
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,220)}《地球脉动》系列\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}just over 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,自那时起 我们的摄影团队走遍了世界各地\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Since then, our camera teams have filmed all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,调查了一些最原始 最偏僻的角落\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and visited some of its wildest and most remote corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,然而事实上 我们拍摄的大多数动物\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}But the truth is that most of the animals we filmed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,都在这20年间变得越来越稀少\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}over these last two decades are now rarer than they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的生存家园\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}And the places where they live
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也面临着越来越大的危机\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}are in greater danger of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些年 我也看到了另一种变化\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}But I've seen another change in those years,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一种充满希望的变化\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}a hopeful change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一代杰出的人们正在挺身而出\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}A new generation of remarkable people are stepping up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救野生动物\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}to save wildlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们克服巨大障碍\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}They're overcoming huge obstacles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,投身危险之境\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}travelling to dangerous places,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有时甚至冒着生命危险\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and sometimes even risking their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说 他们是真正的英雄\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}To me, they are true heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,本集将讲述这些英雄的故事\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}This is the story of some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,安第斯山脉深处\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Hidden in the heart of the Andes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,隐藏着詹巴图研究中心\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}is the Centro Jambatu research centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,它正在保护一些 也许会令人惊讶的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}It's protecting members of what is, perhaps surprisingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最濒危的动物群体\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}the most endangered group of animals in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,青蛙\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是各自物种中 仅存的一些个体\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}These individuals are the very last of their particular species.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它们被带到这里的目的 不只是保护它们\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}They're brought here not only for protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,更重要的是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}but, more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让种群繁衍壮大\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}to increase their numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而找到它们的人是\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}And the person to find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哈梅 · 库莱布拉斯\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..Jaime Culebras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}我第一次见到青蛙时 只有7岁\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}I was seven the first time that I saw a frog
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}那一刻改变了我的一生\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}and just changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,自那之后\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}And ever since his childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直在探索最偏远的地方\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}he's been exploring the remotest places
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找最稀有的青蛙\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and searching for the rarest frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}这是只叶蛙\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}This is a leaf frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}它太奇妙了\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}He is just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}看到这样的动物 怎么能不爱它呢\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}It's impossible to don't fall in love with an animal like this, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有一只青蛙非常特别\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}But there is one frog here that is very special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,名字叫做悲情圣地亚哥\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}His name, Sad Santiago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}这是悲情圣地亚哥\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}This is Sad Santiago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}悲情是因为它非常孤单\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}He's sad because he's alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}它是物种中的最后一员之一\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}He's one of the last members of his species.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}它需要一只雌性伴侣\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}And he needs a female.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,莫罗纳-圣地亚哥丑角蛙\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Known as the Morona-Santiago harlequin frog,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它可能是世界上最稀有的青蛙\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}he may be the rarest frog in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的其他青蛙都在尽可能\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}While the other frogs here are doing their best
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,增加种群数量\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}to increase their populations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,悲情圣地亚哥却孤零零等了四年\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Santiago has sat alone for four long years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}也许它不是最漂亮的青蛙 但也值得被爱\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Maybe it's not the most beautiful frog, but he deserves love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,悲情圣地亚哥已经老了\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Santiago has now grown old,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果哈梅不能尽快为它找到伴侣\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and if Jaime can't find a female for him soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,整个物种便可能就此灭绝\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}the whole species could become extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这种青蛙最后的目击地点\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}The last place where one of these frogs was seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是在厄瓜多尔云雾森林的高山上\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..was high up on a mountain in the cloud forest of Ecuador.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,路只有一条\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}There's only one way to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一同前往的还有青蛙猎人达尔文\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Joining him is fellow frog-hunter Darwin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,以及哈梅的伴侣 青蛙学家弗朗西斯卡\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and Jaime's partner and frog scientist, Francesca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}哦\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}快点\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Come on, vamanos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}上去\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Arriba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}这是地球上最潮湿的地方之一\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}This is one of the wettest places on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}而且现在正是雨季\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}and right now it's actually the wet season, the rainy season,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}雨水更多\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}so it rains even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,潮湿且到处都是虫子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Soaking wet and teeming with bugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是青蛙的理想家园\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..it's a perfect place for frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}出发\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大多数青蛙夜晚才会现身\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Most frogs come out of hiding at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}这个地方太奇妙了\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}This place is extremely wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:08:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}但需要时刻小心\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}But you have to be careful where you put your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}和他在一起\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Being with him is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}很特别\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}..it's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}这段关系很特别\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}It's not your regular relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}他对青蛙非常着迷\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Oh, he's obsessed. He's really obsessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的溪流可能隐藏着许多\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Streams like this should be full of frogs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,各种各样的青蛙\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}of many different species...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们找了整夜 却一无所获\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..but they search all night and find nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}整片森林鸦雀无声\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}It's a silent forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}很悲哀\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}It's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,青蛙的歌声 正渐渐消逝\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}The sound of frogs is slowly disappearing from our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:09:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如今 很多青蛙物种\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}The only place many frog species can now be found
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只能在博物馆中找到\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}is in a museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一个关键原因 在于一种叫做壶菌的真菌的蔓延\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}A key reason is the spread of a fungus called chytrid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它能寄生在青蛙的湿润皮肤上\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..that can grow on the moist skins of frogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,最终致其死亡\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}eventually killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,据估计 90种青蛙因此而灭绝\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}90 species are thought to have become extinct as a consequence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还有近600种青蛙 正面临极高的灭绝风险\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and almost 600 more are now critically endangered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}如果没有壶菌 我敢保证\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Before chytrid, I'm pretty sure that you could walk
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}这条小溪将到处都是\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}through the stream and see everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}趴在石头上的各种青蛙\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}many, many, many frogs on the rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}呱呱大叫\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}calling "prrr-prrr"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}我多希望我生活在壶菌病之前\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}I wish I had been born before the frog disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,夜复一夜\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Night after night...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在小溪四处搜寻\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..they search the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}哈梅\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Jaime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,终于 有了一个发现\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}At last, there is a discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}声音是\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}The sound is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}我不确定具体在哪 但大概就在这里\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}I don't know exactly where, but it's there, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}在水里\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}En el agua!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}抓到了\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}We have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}一只玻璃蛙\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}A glass frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}一只非常漂亮的玻璃蛙\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}A really beautiful glass frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,玻璃蛙如今越来越稀少\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Glass frogs are becoming increasingly rare,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也许某一天便会彻底灭绝\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and one day they, too, could disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但团队寻找的目标不是它\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}But it's not what they are looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 很多物种悄无声息地灭绝\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}The fact is that countless species go extinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,鲜有人知\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈梅唯一能做的 便是继续寻找\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}All Jaime can do is to continue his search
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,悲情圣地亚哥的伴侣\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}for a mate for Santiago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}在那里吗\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}It's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}我找到了一只雌性\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}I found a female!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}啊\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}太棒了\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}是只雌性 看啊\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}It's a female! Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}体型比雄性大一些\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}The size is bigger than the males.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}哇\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}我太高兴了\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}I feel so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}第一只雌性\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}The first female!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这只雌蛙将成为新繁殖计划的关键\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}She could be the cornerstone of a new breeding programme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}悲情圣地亚哥彻底不悲情了\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Santiago will be very, very, very, very, very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}这只雌蛙特别漂亮\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Because she's really beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}我手上拎着希望\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}In my hand, I have hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}是这个物种的救星\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}I have the saviour of this species,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}也是繁殖计划的救星\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}for breeding programmes and for people to reproduce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}说不清 感觉希望就捧在我手上\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}I don't know, it's like I just have hope in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,世上有7000多种青蛙\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}There are over 7,000 species of frogs in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会有人疑惑\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and you may well ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就算有几种消失了 又有什么大不了的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..does it really matter if a few go extinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 看看这种小小的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Well, just look at this tiny species
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,箭毒蛙\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}of poison arrow frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,科学家发现它皮肤上的化学物质\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Scientists discovered a chemical on its skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,镇痛效果是吗啡的200倍\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..200 times stronger than morphine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如今科学家正在深入研究 以开发强效止痛药\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Now they are studying how it works to create powerful new painkillers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但大自然远不只是一个药箱那么简单\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}But the natural world is not just one vast medicine chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,它有着无可替代的重要性\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}It's far more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大自然是我们的生命之源\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}It is our life support system,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是世界的基石\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}the fabric that holds our world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们失去了大自然的一部分\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Remove a part of it, a species or a habitat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,将会造成未知的后果\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and there's no knowing what could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,典型的例子 非洲森林象\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}A prime example is the forest elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是非洲雨林的\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}They play a crucial role in maintaining
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,重要组成部分\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}the rainforests of Africa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它们帮助植物传播种子\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..dispersing seeds and making clearings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为其他动物创造生存空间\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}that are then used by many other animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,2004年 我们为第一部《地球脉动》\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}We filmed these images in 2004
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,拍摄了这些画面\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}for the first Planet Earth series.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,九年后 偷猎者为了象牙\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Nine years later, poachers came here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,猎杀了26头森林象\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}and killed 26 elephants for their ivory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,其中还有4只小象\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..including four of the calves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,自那之后\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Since that first series,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,非洲森林象的数量\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}the number of forest elephants across Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,减少了三分之二\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}has dropped by two-thirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但阻止偷猎的工作十分危险\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}But stopping the slaughter is a risky business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,非洲西部 科特迪瓦 阿比让\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Abidjan, in Cote d'Ivoire, West Africa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是非法象牙交易的一个节点\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}..part of the global network in the illegal ivory trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一名女性来到此处\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}A stranger has flown in from Vietnam,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她来自象牙的重要进口国 越南\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}a hub for the import of ivory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}大象是我最爱的动物\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Elephant is my favourite animal on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}看到它们这样被猎杀\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Seeing how they are being killed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}真的很让我难过\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}that just really upset me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}我想做些力所能及的事情\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}and I just want to do something - anything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她的名字是阮庄\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Her name - Trang Nguyen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她假装是象牙买家\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Her speciality - infiltrating the illegal wildlife trade
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,打入非法野生动物交易内部\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}by posing as a buyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}我得稍微改变一下性格\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}I have to change my character a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}因为通常我很健谈\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}because normally I'm very chatty
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}喜欢笑 喜欢与人交谈\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}and I like to smile, and I like to talk to people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}但我必须变得冷漠刻薄\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}but I have to be cold, and I have to be mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}你身边都是罪犯\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}When you're going in, you're dealing with criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}依靠谎话\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}You're telling lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}假装自己是一个买家\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}You have to pretend to be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}如果不小心露馅了\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}If by accident you blow that cover
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}很可能就没命了\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}it's possible that I'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,阮庄和一个叫EAGLE的保护组织合作\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Trang is working with a network of conservationists called EAGLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她的联络人是伦斯 · 伊尔根\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Her contact here is Rens Ilgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}这里的象牙交易有个特点\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}But what is particular with this new trade in West Africa is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}很多象牙都是小象的\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}as you can see, a lot of the tusks are from baby elephants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}这说明 幸存的大象已经所剩无几了\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}So, they're really down to the last elephants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}上周 有七个人被杀\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Last week, seven people were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}七个护林员被杀吗\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}Seven ranger was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}所以显然 如今已经不仅是象牙交易的问题\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}So, clearly, it is not just about the ivory trade,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}还有很多无辜的人 为了保护大象而失去生命\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}but a lot of people, rangers, that are being killed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}-简直是一场战争 -一场战争\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}It's...it's war. It's war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}-连刚出生的小象也不放过 -是啊\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}And they're even going for the baby elephants.  Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在阮庄确定了自己的任务\N{\fs12\1c&HFFFF80&\b0}Now Trang is set her task.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}我希望你去见见象牙交易的首领\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}So, I want you to meet the godfather of ivory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}四年前 他因藏有400公斤象牙\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}We already arrested him four years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}而被逮捕过一次\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}when he had 400kg of ivory,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}那些象牙是提供给越南的\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}which he was supplying to the Vietnamese community
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}与当地黑帮有所牵连\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}linked to the Vietnamese mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFF80&}因为被抓过 所以他可能会很谨慎\N{\fs12\1c&H00FFFFFF\b0}As he has been arrested before, he might be very cautious.
